{
  "stem": "7337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the day that I came out, we left Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, his plans were to leave Germany in 1932.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By 1932, he had moved all his money officially, and through the official sources-- the banks-- into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in 1932, the then finance minister Bruening brought out exchange control, which forbade any resident in Germany to have accounts outside Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother's health had deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was operated in 1932.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when they discovered that she had cancer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the doctors advised my father that he could not move her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He would have to stay near the hospital where the professor who operated was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] situation became so dangerous for my father that he said he must bring the money back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He can't live in Germany, having transferred his money out officially through the banks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was known that he had done so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he brought his entire fortune back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he made arrangements that should he ever leave, the French consul would move whatever cash he gave him for 25% into France.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my father took all the cash that he had been able to accumulate from 1928 onward, and kept it in numerous private bank accounts.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kept transferring from one to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on every transfer he pulled some money out into cash, which he put into safes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he had the larger portion of his money was in cash.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was able to move that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But his fixed assets, of course, he lost-- he left behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Buildings, our apartment, the real estate that he owned, the factories that he owned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those he just lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
